{
  "bookId": "laozi-wangbi-wiki",
  "num": 65,
  "title": "第六十五章",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "古之善為道者，非以明民，將以愚之。"
    },
    {
      "text": "民之難治，以其智多。"
    },
    {
      "text": "故以智治國，國之賊，"
    },
    {
      "text": "不以智治國，國之福。知此兩者亦稽式。常知稽式，是謂玄德。玄德深矣，遠矣，"
    },
    {
      "text": "與物反矣，"
    },
    {
      "text": "然後乃至大順。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "wangbi": [
      {
        "id": "wangbi-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 17
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "明謂多見巧詐，蔽其樸也。愚謂無知守真，順自然也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "多智巧詐，故難治也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 2,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 10
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "智，猶治也，以智而治國，所以謂之賊者，故謂之智也。民之難治，以其多智也，當務塞兌閉門，令無知無欲，而以智術動民。邪心既動，復以巧術防民之偽，民知其術，防隨而避之，思惟密巧，奸偽益滋，故曰，以智治國，國之賊也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 3,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 36
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "稽，同也。今古之所同，則而不可廢，能知稽式，是謂玄德，玄德深矣，遠矣。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-5",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "反其真也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
